Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,PART-B
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好羡慕啊    妖精那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还能开庆功宴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,见面后要被炫耀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,羡慕嫉妒恨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也不能认输
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:01:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,早晚要超过她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有干劲    有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.75,0:02:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥    稍微闭下眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可以睁开啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微逞了逞能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉就像新婚一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,今天妖精庆功宴的直播
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就拜托了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害    豪华炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去开开眼界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,村征小姐也办过庆功宴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是狮童国光啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,大家近来都还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,还是一样地赶不上她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,都到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,来给好友捧个场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天怎么样啊    是不是美得不要不要的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊    埃罗芒阿老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认识叫这个名字的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜你    妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是    我们的一点心意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,里面是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,山田妖精老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你    和泉正宗老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,东西放在这里可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,今天    你妈妈也来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,请帖送出去她就过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈一直最爱我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是很爱你妈妈的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,待会儿把她也介绍给你认识
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也该出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮我    脱下礼服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人脱不下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫其他人来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,屁屁…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你难道没穿…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,啥！？    穿…穿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,小…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,小？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小一点而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是    是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这    这里也要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这个场景之前也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这…这是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,算了    今天还是少喝点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,正宗君真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,村征酱    去那边
